title: Composite tool for winglet manufacturing
objective: An all composite tool for the manufacturing of winglet pairs will be designed and manufactured. The tool will be self heated. Separate cavities will be fed by a single injection system, ensuring identical quality and dimensional tolerances for both winglets.
